{"tid":1450970,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T18:08:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T01:08:30.000Z","uid":258402,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"79feeb630f27652d7f7d0d697fe48a79efa46d2b","tid":1450970,"uid":258402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:08:52.000Z","msg":"一人一 狂洗連登post [時事台]<br />\n唔該你出一份力，肯出post，聽日就係人都知入機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n標題：「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=bqZDxu8XrC4QaJB2SmgqvooeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=cdc21b09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=bqZDxu8XrC4QaJB2SmgqvooeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=16f9f644\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a><br />\n3448<br />\n76"},{"pid":"e612ed1fea78b89c43e4e2ff2af44bf6e48c76ba","tid":1450970,"uid":258402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:09:55.000Z","msg":"推到五大訴求全部實現"},{"pid":"f9f1c4aad7839d0849d99442f2f649529b0cd3ef","tid":1450970,"uid":89873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:10:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f664dfe931118c38f47e2db4daad10434c66f48a","tid":1450970,"uid":258402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:10:10.000Z","msg":"推到有公義"},{"pid":"bc98fcc7858f4107867930b7a2aa09787fc02ae7","tid":1450970,"uid":258402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"